      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question. im taking sertraline for my mood but finals week is coming up and i feel super low and drained. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost things naturally since its just a herb. is that cool to mix with the sertraline? i dont want to take more pills if i dont have to lol",
