    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i feel like i know my body... i've read a lot about how st johns wort is basically just a mild plant supplement and most people use it for minor stuff without issues. sertraline is a pretty heavy drug so maybe i should just stick to the natural stuff + a lower dose of the sertraline? do u really think a little bit of the herb would cause something as bad as serotonin syndrome?",
