      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Relying on general knowledge about herbal supplements can be dangerous when mixing them with prescription medications like sertraline, as even small doses significantly alter serotonin levels. Serotonin syndrome is a serious medical emergency that can occur from these interactions, regardless of how \"mild\" people perceive St. John's Wort to be. Please do not adjust your medication or add supplements without explicit approval from your prescribing doctor who can monitor your specific risk. Your safety is more important than avoiding extra pills.",
