      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it's hard to get an appointment with my doctor before my exams start next week. i'm just really struggling to focus. if i just take a very small amount, like half a dose of the st johns wort, it shouldn't really impact the sertraline that much right? it seems like a reasonable way to get a little extra help without it being a big medical thing.",
